  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h4>
<p>To upgrade from 3.15.3 to 3.15.9 in a singleton deployment, follow these steps:</p>
<ol>
 <li>
  <p>Stop Hybrid Chat</p>
  <code-snippet class="theme-code-snippet">
   <div class="theme-code-snippet-header">Bash</div>
   <scroll-shadow>
    <div data-component="code" data-language="bash">
     <pre><code>efutils all down
</code></pre>
    </div>
   </scroll-shadow>
   <copy-clipboard class="theme-code-snippet-copy">
    <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-copy_content copy-icon">
     <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#copy_content"></use>
    </svg>
   </copy-clipboard>
  </code-snippet>
  <p>
   <br>
  </p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Navigate to the HC installation directory</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Create a backup of the <code>coreversion.env</code>&nbsp; file&nbsp;</p>
  <code-snippet class="theme-code-snippet">
   <div class="theme-code-snippet-header">Bash</div>
   <scroll-shadow>
    <div data-component="code" data-language="bash">
     <pre><code># The following command will rename coreversion.env file as coreversion.env.3.15.3.backup
mv coreversion.env{,.3.15.3.backup}
</code></pre>
    </div>
   </scroll-shadow>
   <copy-clipboard class="theme-code-snippet-copy">
    <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-copy_content copy-icon">
     <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#copy_content"></use>
    </svg>
   </copy-clipboard>
  </code-snippet>
  <p>
   <br>
  </p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>Download the updated coreversion.env file&nbsp;</p>
  <code-snippet class="theme-code-snippet">
   <div class="theme-code-snippet-header">Bash</div>
   <scroll-shadow>
    <div data-component="code" data-language="bash">
     <pre><code># This command must be executed in the HC installation directory which you navigated to following step 2
# Using curl
curl https://gitlab.expertflow.com/expertflow/hybrid-chat/-/raw/3.15.9/coreversion.env --output coreversion.env

# or via using wget
wget https://gitlab.expertflow.com/expertflow/hybrid-chat/-/raw/3.15.9/coreversion.env
</code></pre>
    </div>
   </scroll-shadow>
   <copy-clipboard class="theme-code-snippet-copy">
    <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-copy_content copy-icon">
     <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#copy_content"></use>
    </svg>
   </copy-clipboard>
  </code-snippet>
  <p>
   <br>
  </p>
  <div data-component="panel" role="note" data-appearance="warning">
   <div class="panel-content">
    <p>The following section of point # 4 only applies if the above commands fail</p>
   </div>
  </div>
  <p>
   <br>
   Executing the above command will fetch updated information about images. If unable to perform this, revert the step 3&nbsp;
  </p>
  <p>
   <br>
  </p>
  <code-snippet class="theme-code-snippet">
